        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="item-label">AyÄ±rÄ±cÄ±lar</span>
          <span class="item-value">Yeni satÄ±r, virgÃ¼l</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="item-label">Maksimum</span>
          <span class="item-value">SÄ±nÄ±r yok</span>
